high_descs: Take an apple out of the microwave.
Bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the apple to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, and walk to the microwave on your right.
Pick up an apple from the microwave.
Turn right, then walk towards the fridge.
Cool the apple inside of the fridge.
Turn around and walk back towards the microwave.
Place the apple back inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled apple inside of a microwave.

high_descs: Walk straight to the table then turn right and walk over to the microwave so you are standing directly in front of it facing it.
Open the microwave and take out the apple that's nearest the back of the microwave and close it again.
Turn right and head over to the fridge and stand so you are directly in front of it facing it.

Open the fridge and put the apple in the back left corner of the shelf on the right side with the brown plate then close the fridge and let it cool for a while before taking it back out and closing the fridge again.
Walk back over to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave to the left of the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in the microwave.
